    <who name="Florian Weimer">fweimer</who>
    <bug_when>2017-02-14 11:05:59 -0500</bug_when>
    <thetext>When USE_BROADCAST is enabled, ypbind pokes at internal glibc data structures (such as struct cu_data), which is not guaranteed to work at all.

Furthermore, the processing in ping_all takes the first reply from any server, but does not verify that it indicates success.  This means that ypbind can easily choose a server which is not currently available.</thetext>
  </long_desc><long_desc isprivate="0" >
